<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Event Showcase</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/swiper@11/swiper-bundle.min.css" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.1/css/all.min.css" integrity="sha512-DTOQO9RWCH3ppGqcWaEA1BIZOC6xxalwEsw9c2QQeAIftl+Vegovlnee1c9QX4TctnWMn13TZye+giMm8e2LwA==" crossorigin="anonymous" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" />
  <link rel="shortcut icon" href="favicon/favicon.ico" type="image/x-icon">
  <style>
    @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Marhey:wght@300..700&family=Montserrat:ital,wght@0,100..900;1,100..900&family=Raleway:ital,wght@0,100..900;1,100..900&display=swap');
    @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Caveat:wght@500&display=swap');
    @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat&display=swap');
    @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Bad+Script&family=Charm&family=Leckerli+One&family=Open+Sans:wght@300&family=Satisfy&display=swap');
    @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Ephesis&display=swap');
    @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Raleway:ital,wght@0,100..900;1,100..900&display=swap');
    @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Marhey:wght@300..700&family=Raleway:ital,wght@0,100..900;1,100..900&display=swap');

    body {
      font-family: "Montserrat", sans-serif;
      font-optical-sizing: auto;
      font-weight: 300;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-image: url(../res/bg.jpg);
      color: #fff;
      position: relative;
      background-attachment: fixed;
      background-repeat: no-repeat;
      background-size: cover;
      min-height: 100vh;
      background-position: center;
    }

    header {
      background-color: #0000006c;
      font-family: "Marhey", sans-serif;
    }

    .logoDiv {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      height: 150px;
    }

    .logo {
      max-width: 200px;
    }

    header li {
      list-style: none;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      font-family: var(--main-font);
    }

    header a {
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #fff;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      font-family: var(--main-font);
      font-weight: var(--main-weight-a);
      padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
      border: none;
      outline: none;
      border-radius: 20px;
    }

    a:hover {
      color: orange;
    }

    header {
      position: relative;
      padding: 0 2rem;
    }

    .navbar {
      width: 100%;
      height: 75px;
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
    }

    .navbar .links {
      display: flex;
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    .navbar .toggle_btn {
      color: #fff;
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      cursor: pointer;
      display: none;
    }

    .action_btn {
      background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.273);
      font-family: var(--main-font);
      color: rgb(255, 248, 125);
      padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
      border: none;
      outline: none;
      border-radius: 20px;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      font-weight: bold;
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    .action_btn:hover {
      scale: 1.05;
      color: #fff;
    }

    .action_btn:active {
      scale: 0.95;
    }

    .dropdown_menu {
      display: none;
      position: absolute;
      right: 2rem;
      top: 60px;
      height: 0;
      width: 300px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.021);
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
      border-radius: 10px;
      overflow: hidden;
      transition: height 0.2s cubic-bezier(0.175, 0.885, 0.32, 1.275);
      z-index: 3;
    }

    .dropdown_menu.open {
      height: 240px;
    }

    .dropdown_menu li {
      padding: 5px 0.5rem;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .dropdown_menu .action_btn {
      width: 100%;
      display: flex;
      background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.536);
      color: rgb(255, 248, 125);
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .dropdown_menu .dd_btn {
      width: 100%;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      background-color: #ffffff00;
    }


    @media(max-width: 992px) {

      .navbar .links,
      .navbar .action_btn {
        display: none;
      }

      .navbar .toggle_btn {
        display: block;
      }

      .dropdown_menu {
        display: block;

      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 576px) {
      .dropdown_menu {
        left: 2rem;
        width: unset;
      }
    }

    .container {
      margin: 5vmin;
      padding: 6vmin;
      background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.580);
      border-radius: 17px;
    }

    .enroll {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: left;
      align-items: last baseline;
      height: 100px;
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }

    .regButton {
      padding: 5px 20px;
      font-family: "Marhey", sans-serif;
      font-size: 20px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border: 0px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      background-color: #3498db;
      color: #fff;
      text-shadow: 2px 2px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.603);
      box-shadow: 2px 2px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.603);
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <header>
    <div class="navbar">
      <div class="logoDiv"><img src="../res/logo.png" alt="logo" class="logo"></div>
      <ul class="links">
        <li><a href="/events">Events</a></li>
        <li><a href="/caportal">CA Portal</a></li>
        <li><a href="/sponsor">Sponsors</a></li>
      </ul>
      <a href="/profile" class="action_btn">profile</a>
      <div class="toggle_btn">
        <i class="fa-solid fa-bars"></i>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="dropdown_menu">
      <li><a href="/events" class="dd_btn">Events</a></li>
      <li><a href="/caportal" class="dd_btn">CA Portal</a></li>
      <li><a href="/sponsor" class="dd_btn">Sponsors</a></li>
      <li><a href="/profile" class="action_btn">profile</a></li>
    </div>
  </header>
  </header>


  <div class="container">
    <div class="heading">
      <h1>Treasure Hunt</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="heading">
      <h2>Rulebook</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      1.Team Formation:<br>

      - Teams should consist of a minimum of two and a maximum of five participants.<br>

      - Each team must choose a unique and creative team name.<br><br>



      2. Starting Point:<br>

      - All teams will gather at the designated starting point at the specified time.<br>

      - A representative from each team will receive the first clue.<br><br>



      3. Clue System:<br>

      - Teams must follow the clues provided sequentially to progress through the treasure hunt.<br>

      - Clues will lead teams to different locations within the event area.<br>

      - Their will be tasks as well in the treasure which have to be completed within the give time. <br><br>


      4. Time Limit:<br>

      - The treasure hunt has a designated time limit for completion.<br>

      - Teams must return to the finish line before the specified deadline.<br><br>



      5. Treasure Collection:<br>

      - At each marked location, teams will find a piece of the treasure or a clue to the next location.<br>

      - Teams must collect all pieces to complete the treasure hunt.<br><br>



      6. Fair Play:<br>

      - No interference with other teams is allowed.<br>

      - Teams caught violating fair play rules may be disqualified.<br><br>



      7. Safety Guidelines:<br>

      - Participants must follow all safety guidelines provided by the event organizers.<br>

      - Teams should avoid dangerous areas or activities during the treasure hunt.<br><br>



      8. Dispute Resolution:<br>

      - In case of disputes or rule clarifications, teams can approach event organizers for resolution.<br>

      - Organizer decisions are final.<br><br>



      9. Finishing:<br>

      - Teams must return to the finish line within the specified time with all collected pieces to qualify for prizes.<br>

      - The theme of the treasure hunt will be revealed on spot. <br><br>



      10. Prizes:<br>

      - Prizes will be awarded based on factors such as completion time and creativity.<br><br>


    </div>
    <div class="enroll">
      <a href="/enrolling/treasure_hunt" class="regButton"><%=BtnName%></a>
    </div>
  </div>


  <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/536b7f8348.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
  <script>
    const toggleBtn = document.querySelector('.toggle_btn')
    const toggleBtnTcon = document.querySelector('.toggle_btn i')
    const dropDownMenu = document.querySelector('.dropdown_menu')

    toggleBtn.onclick = function() {
      dropDownMenu.classList.toggle('open')
    }
  </script>
</body>

</html>